STEP File Viewer - Part with graphical PMI

The visualization was generated by the NIST STEP File Analyzer and Viewer. More Viewer examples are available here. The STEP file was generated from one of the NIST CAD models. Key 'a' to view all, 'r' to restore, Page Up for orthographic. Use the mouse in 'Examine Mode' to rotate, pan, zoom.
